Package: simstonk
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Investment Portfolios
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lawrence R. De Geest
Maintainer: Lawrence R. De Geest <lrdegeest@gmail.com>
Description: Run a Monte Carlo simulation for an investment. 
    Simulations are based on ordered draws of historical data.
    365 consecutive days holding an asset, two consecutive years, and so on.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: 
  dplyr, 
  ggplot2, 
  tidyquant
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
